data.description: AVAILABLE NOW! Introducing a stunning modern home built meticulously crafted in 2021. From the moment you step inside, you are greeted by an abundance of natural light in the open-concept living spaces. The thoughtfully designed layout boasts spacious rooms, and a harmonious flow, creating an inviting atmosphere for both relaxation and entertainment. This home has 3 bedrooms plus a FLEX SPACE that can also be used as a 4th bedroom. Situated in a desirable location, you will have access to all the sought after Manor amenities and activities.
